            <div type="letter" xml:id="letter_1672_xx_01_mm2os_raw" n="07" facs="DSCF8224">
                <head type="raw" xml:lang="fr" />
                <note resp="#smn">
                [[Speculating that it could have been written on August 1, 1672. The letter says "ce pre[[…]] 1672," and it was written from Grenoble. Marie wrote a letter to Lorenzo from Grenoble, dated "ce premier aout 1672" with similar-looking ink lines (DSCF8469-DSCF8471). Perhaps she just neglected to write "ao&#251;t" on the letter she wrote to Ortensia?]]
                </note>
                <note resp="#smn" xml:id="archive-note">
                Collocazione II-C.P.1. lett. 7
                Lettere di Maria Mancini – 1672
                Contessa Stella
                Numero d'ordine – 7

                Donna Maria Mancini-Colonna

                =

                Lettera alla Contessa Ortensia Stella
                in data	10 [["Gennaio" erased]] 1672 da Grenoble
                Sigillo – tutta di pugno –

                oggetto:
                </note>
                <pb facs="DSCF8225"/>
                <note resp="#smn">
                [[On the left side of the image, the diagonally folded paper with address written on outside: 
                "Alla Sig[[nora]]
                Contessa Stella 
                Roma"
                + 1 red wax seal]]
                </note>
                <note resp="#smn">
                [[On the right half of the sheet:]]    
                </note>
                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <placeName key="grenoble">grenoble</placeName>
                        <date when="1672-08-07">ce pre[[?]] 1672</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Jey sceu par mon frere qu'andrea servoit les anfans ce pourquoye ne me l'envoy&#233; point car ie suis ravie quil soit a eux mon frere et icy depuis trois iours ; souvenes vous de m'envoyer tiche et costance car ie ne saure plus durer avec une fille toutte seule; embrasses mes enfans pour moy et salue anna aquittes vous des comisions que ie vous done si vous voules que ie continue a croire que vous aym&#233; la </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed><persName key="mancini-marie">C. C.</persName></signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
